item.title: Tutorial to add summoning on testscape?
item.dc:creator: @Jammy Jammy
item.description:
@Jammy wrote:

That amount of errors usually means that there is a } bracket missing or are to many } brackets in the code. To find the section of code go to the top error on the compile and find that. Check that and try re-compiling.
